                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-655045077" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="655045077">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aubonpain/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">之前在家放在洗手间用两年时间才读完。来到美国后对书中很多内容有了更深的理解，很想再读一遍。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
